class EventSequence(data, config=None, alphabet=None)
A sequence of discrete events at specific time points (not all time steps need to have an event). Useful for event-history data.

Trajectory / TrajectoryPool
class Trajectory(data, config=None, alphabet=None)
class TrajectoryPool(data, config=None, alphabet=None)
Time-stamped variants of StateSequence / SequencePool for data where time steps are actual timestamps rather than integer indices. API mirrors StateSequence / SequencePool.

